Package: dataduck
Title: Tools for Data Bucketing, Aggregation, and Validation Optimized for Databases
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lorae", "Stojanovic", , "stojanovic.lorae@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides functions for data bucketing using lookup tables, data aggregation, and validation, 
    with a specific focus on optimizing performance when working with databases like DuckDB. The package
    includes tools for creating custom buckets of continuous or categorical variables, calculating weighted
    means, and producing simple visualizations using `ggplot2`.
